00:00:47,380 --> 00:00:51,180
=Episode 9=

14
00:00:52,760 --> 00:00:56,640
Before you die,
you have to do me a small favor.

15
00:00:59,760 --> 00:01:01,240
(No, Chen Qi hasn't arrived yet.)

16
00:01:01,520 --> 00:01:03,760
(I can't save Miss Ouyang on my own.)

17
00:01:04,200 --> 00:01:05,640
Here.

18
00:01:06,160 --> 00:01:07,480
Sign this.

19
00:01:07,480 --> 00:01:09,460
(Equity Transfer Agreement)

20
00:01:10,880 --> 00:01:12,160
In your dreams.

21
00:01:13,810 --> 00:01:14,760
Sign it.

22
00:01:17,680 --> 00:01:19,440
I would rather die than sign it.

23
00:01:21,640 --> 00:01:23,040
Make her sign it.

24
00:01:23,160 --> 00:01:24,160
What are you doing?

25
00:01:26,680 --> 00:01:28,560
Let go of me. Let go.

26
00:01:29,640 --> 00:01:30,640
Let go.

27
00:01:30,880 --> 00:01:31,720
Put your finger on it.

28
00:01:32,040 --> 00:01:33,520
You'll suffer for this.

29
00:01:33,520 --> 00:01:34,920
Let go.

30
00:01:35,160 --> 00:01:36,000
Hurry up.

31
00:01:39,800 --> 00:01:41,040
- Put it on.
- Let go.

32
00:01:44,160 --> 00:01:45,240
Let her go.

33
00:01:48,760 --> 00:01:49,640
I'll stay.

34
00:01:52,040 --> 00:01:54,240
Another daredevil.

35
00:01:54,570 --> 00:01:55,410
Get him.

36
00:02:17,880 --> 00:02:19,120
Qin Jifeng.

37
00:02:25,240 --> 00:02:26,480
Qin Jifeng.

38
00:02:29,880 --> 00:02:31,370
Let go of me.

39
00:02:31,390 --> 00:02:36,230
♪As if time flows♪

40
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:38,040
Let go of me.

41
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:43,830
♪Unable to catch up
with the changing scenery♪

42
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:49,600
Qin Jifeng!

43
00:02:50,600 --> 00:02:52,580
Let go of me.

44
00:02:53,880 --> 00:02:55,240
Qin Jifeng!

45
00:03:02,920 --> 00:03:03,760
Get up!

46
00:03:03,880 --> 00:03:04,720
Get up!

47
00:03:06,480 --> 00:03:07,680
Let go!

48
00:03:08,920 --> 00:03:09,880
Get up!

49
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:11,640
Qin Jifeng!

50
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:16,040
Let go of me.

51
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:25,780
♪Life is too cold, the embrace too warm♪

52
00:03:26,220 --> 00:03:33,110
♪How can fragile petals
withstand the harsh snow♪

53
00:03:33,430 --> 00:03:37,600
♪The dancing light takes away the brilliance♪

54
00:03:37,750 --> 00:03:40,330
♪How can we measure the dissipating youth♪

55
00:03:40,330 --> 00:03:41,680
Qin Jifeng.

56
00:03:41,860 --> 00:03:48,170
♪Looking back, true love never changed♪

57
00:03:49,200 --> 00:03:50,480
Boss, we are here.

58
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:51,980
Boss.

59
00:03:54,720 --> 00:03:56,000
Get them.

60
00:03:56,720 --> 00:03:57,640
Let's go.

61
00:04:03,600 --> 00:04:04,800
Even if I die,

62
00:04:05,160 --> 00:04:06,880
I'll take someone down with me.

63
00:04:09,320 --> 00:04:10,480
Do you know how to shoot?

64
00:04:11,720 --> 00:04:12,760
Do you need me to teach you?

65
00:04:15,760 --> 00:04:17,540
Shoot, do you need me to teach you?

66
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:23,640
Next time you fire a gun, make sure
to check if there are bullets inside.

67
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:26,120
(His gun is out of bullets.)

68
00:04:32,850 --> 00:04:34,280
Qin Jifeng, how are you?

69
00:04:34,280 --> 00:04:35,200
Are you alright?

70
00:04:45,160 --> 00:04:47,490
I'll kill you!

71
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:10,080
Yue!

72
00:05:10,760 --> 00:05:11,680
I've heard everything.

73
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:14,460
Ouyang Shanhai killed your father.

74
00:05:15,480 --> 00:05:18,990
Today, I'll avenge him.

75
00:05:22,300 --> 00:05:23,280
Thank you, Mr. Liang.

76
00:05:26,320 --> 00:05:27,160
Jiahao,

77
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:28,920
take Yue back.

78
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:30,400
Alright, Father.

79
00:05:33,280 --> 00:05:34,720
Yue, it's alright now.

80
00:05:35,360 --> 00:05:36,200
Let's go.

81
00:05:38,280 --> 00:05:39,120
Jiahao,

82
00:05:40,560 --> 00:05:42,040
he saved me today.

83
00:05:42,880 --> 00:05:44,440
I can't just leave him.

84
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:50,640
I understand.

85
00:05:52,320 --> 00:05:53,720
I won't make it difficult for you.

86
00:05:56,320 --> 00:05:57,160
Let's go.

87
00:06:05,720 --> 00:06:07,640
Master, we've searched the outer rooms.

88
00:06:07,640 --> 00:06:08,800
We couldn't find the letter.

89
00:06:09,720 --> 00:06:10,560
Check the inner rooms.

90
00:06:10,910 --> 00:06:12,170
Make sure to find that letter.

91
00:06:12,530 --> 00:06:13,370
Yes.

92
00:06:33,640 --> 00:06:34,480
I'll do it.

93
00:06:45,160 --> 00:06:46,000
Yue,

94
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:48,080
I'm sorry.

95
00:06:58,010 --> 00:06:59,400
I sent a telegram to bring you back.

96
00:07:00,280 --> 00:07:01,480
I didn't want you to miss the chance

97
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:02,960
to bid Mr. Ouyang farewell.

98
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:06,950
I had Chen Qi investigate secretly,

99
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:08,720
hoping to find out

100
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:10,760
how he really died.

101
00:07:15,280 --> 00:07:16,680
Why didn't you say anything when we met?

102
00:07:17,520 --> 00:07:18,680
Why didn't you say anything later?

103
00:07:24,800 --> 00:07:26,680
You are a respectable lady

104
00:07:28,290 --> 00:07:29,520
and I'm a gangster.

105
00:07:30,160 --> 00:07:31,800
Before the truth is uncovered,

106
00:07:32,710 --> 00:07:33,880
I didn't want you to get involved.

107
00:07:38,560 --> 00:07:39,400
Is it worth it?

108
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:43,640
As long as you're safe,

109
00:07:44,280 --> 00:07:45,120
it's worth it.

110
00:07:49,450 --> 00:07:51,060
You've saved me many times already.

111
00:07:52,440 --> 00:07:54,160
You've repaid all your debts.

112
00:07:55,170 --> 00:07:56,700
You don't need to risk yourself
for me anymore.

113
00:07:57,280 --> 00:07:58,240
And there's no need...

114
00:07:58,720 --> 00:07:59,720
Before, it was to repay a debt.

115
00:08:03,280 --> 00:08:04,400
Now, it's not.

116
00:08:05,970 --> 00:08:07,800
♪Between the rise and fall of stars♪

117
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:10,780
♪Rings of time frost the deep feelings♪

118
00:08:10,780 --> 00:08:13,320
♪Wherever it is♪

119
00:08:13,320 --> 00:08:15,160
♪Even if the longing is burning♪

120
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:17,220
♪The bustling world isn't fading♪

121
00:08:17,220 --> 00:08:21,360
♪Can I redeem a period of time♪

122
00:08:21,500 --> 00:08:25,270
♪To spare me a moment with you♪

123
00:08:26,800 --> 00:08:27,640
It's...

124
00:08:31,010 --> 00:08:32,480
I bought it from Mr. Tang's this morning.

125
00:08:33,040 --> 00:08:33,880
Have some.

126
00:08:37,360 --> 00:08:39,080
Sit down. Join me for a meal.

127
00:08:43,670 --> 00:08:45,940
♪While the fallen flowers are still fragrant♪

128
00:08:45,940 --> 00:08:50,600
♪Keep the fate in your heart♪

129
00:08:51,350 --> 00:08:53,300
♪Just because of you, I cherish the youth♪

130
00:08:53,300 --> 00:08:57,030
♪And have dreams♪

131
00:08:58,680 --> 00:09:00,360
♪Mountains and seas don't know our world♪

132
00:09:00,360 --> 00:09:01,200
Be careful, it's hot.

133
00:09:02,520 --> 00:09:05,480
♪How absurd the journey is♪

134
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:10,820
♪If you look back, it's the end of the world♪

135
00:09:10,830 --> 00:09:12,120
Yue.

136
00:09:13,060 --> 00:09:13,980
Yue.

137
00:09:15,430 --> 00:09:16,270
Yue.

138
00:09:19,960 --> 00:09:21,880
Mr. and Mrs. Liang.

139
00:09:22,310 --> 00:09:23,360
What brings you here?

140
00:09:24,280 --> 00:09:25,700
Mr. Liang and I

141
00:09:25,720 --> 00:09:29,490
came here today specifically
to discuss your wedding date.

142
00:09:32,150 --> 00:09:33,240
So soon?

143
00:09:35,270 --> 00:09:38,040
I promised your father to take care of you.

144
00:09:38,710 --> 00:09:40,760
Now that you've avenged your father,

145
00:09:41,180 --> 00:09:42,600
everything is back on track.

146
00:09:43,170 --> 00:09:44,420
It's about time.

147
00:09:50,220 --> 00:09:51,720
Dad, Mom,

148
00:09:53,330 --> 00:09:55,480
there's no rush about the wedding date.

149
00:09:57,250 --> 00:09:58,630
Yue and I haven't discussed it yet.

150
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:02,120
What is there to discuss?

151
00:10:02,560 --> 00:10:03,880
The wedding date cannot be delayed.

152
00:10:04,750 --> 00:10:07,160
Many things need to be prepared in advance.

153
00:10:07,870 --> 00:10:08,760
Recently,

154
00:10:09,760 --> 00:10:10,860
it's not peaceful.

155
00:10:12,060 --> 00:10:13,440
Hongcheng is also very chaotic.

156
00:10:14,190 --> 00:10:15,720
If you want to make a name in Hongcheng

157
00:10:16,080 --> 00:10:18,080
and manage Fortune Trading Company well,

158
00:10:18,850 --> 00:10:22,170
you will need my support.

159
00:10:22,680 --> 00:10:23,520
Yue,

160
00:10:24,160 --> 00:10:25,400
don't you agree?

161
00:10:31,200 --> 00:10:32,040
Dad,

162
00:10:32,640 --> 00:10:33,840
Yue and I have plans.

163
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:35,240
I'm asking Yue.

164
